        Clause 50 [<span class="italic">Adoption by one person</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0637P0-03023'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0637P0_20020711_GCR_82' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendments Nos. 74 and 75 not moved.</span>]
